          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Ge(Li) detector, located in the horizontal",
                "plane at an angle of 0 deg. to the beam axis was used",
                "to register gamma-radiation with energies of",
                "400...5000 keV. The resolution of the Ge(Li) detector",
                "was 2.5 keV for gamma-quanta with an energy of",
                "1332 keV, and its efficiency was equivalent to 19%,",
                "relative to a 7.5 by 7.5 cm NaI(Tl) detector."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The NaI(Tl) scintillation detector with a",
                "crystal volume of 160 cm3. NaI(Tl) , a large-volume",
                "detector, was also used to detect the high-energy",
                "gamma-radiation with energies of 4000...17000 keV",
                "NaI(Tl) detector was installed vertically above the",
                "target at an angle of 90 deg. relative to the",
                "direction of the proton beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was prepared in the form of tablet from",
                "powder of boron of natural isotopic composition of",
                "9 mm in diameter and 2 mm of thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
